WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.200
O Sheikh Zayd,

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:05.000
how can I attain humility in my prayer?

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Humility,

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.000
is a result.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:12.500
It is knowledge that settles in a person,

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.500
and affects them,

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:17.200
leading to God-consciousness,

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:18.999
which then leads to humility.
